# Windsurf Rules: EduStack Smart Backend

## Stack
- PHP 8.5 / Laravel 13 / Inertia.js v2 + React 19 / TailwindCSS v4 / Pest v4

## Modular Architecture (MANDATORY)

All modules: `app/Modules/<Module>/`

```
├── Domain/Contracts/       # Interfaces
├── Domain/Policies/        # Policies
├── Domain/Rules/           # Validation
├── Application/DTOs/       # DTOs
├── Application/UseCases/Command/  # Writes
├── Application/UseCases/Query/    # Reads
├── Application/Support/    # Mappers
├── Infrastructure/Repositories/   # Eloquent
├── Infrastructure/Queries/Options/ # QueryBuilder config
├── Infrastructure/Analytics/      # Integrations
├── Http/Controllers/       # Thin
├── Http/Requests/          # FormRequests
├── Http/Resources/         # API Resources
├── Providers/              # DI, policies, routes
└── routes/                 # Routes
```

### Rules
1. NO Services — UseCases only
2. Thin controllers
3. Repository pattern
4. DI via Providers
5. QueryBuilder via Options classes
6. DTOs in Application/DTOs
7. Architecture tests per module

## Conventions
- PHP 8 constructor promotion, explicit types
- Form Requests, Eloquent, eager loading
- Pest testing
- `vendor/bin/pint` for formatting
